### Create Author
POST http://localhost:8080/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Robert Martin",
  "email": "robert@gmail.com",
  "bio": "Author of Clean Code"
}

### Create Book
POST http://localhost:8080/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code",
  "isbn": "978-0132350884",
  "available": true
}

### Create Member
POST http://localhost:8080/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Anjan",
  "email": "anjan@gmail.com",
  "phone": "314-000-0000"
}

### Borrow book
POST http://localhost:8080/members/1/borrow/1

### Get all books
GET http://localhost:8080/books

### Search books
GET http://localhost:8080/books/search?title=clean